[ul][center][IMG]http://i47.tinypic.com/29q1q93.png[/img]
[IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/ne8dx3.gif[/img] [IMG]http://i48.tinypic.com/xm7ryq.gif[/img] [/center] [center] FOR VIDEOS AND UPDATES GO TO: [url=http://www.youtube.com/user/PJAnnihilation]http://www.youtube.com/user/PJAnnihilation[/url] [color=orange] [B][/center]
[b]Hey, reader and welcome to the official project annihilation thread :D
This is a new and upcoming server that would blow your mind! It will have more features than many servers in the rsps community!
It is built to Annihilate any server in its way by showing a stellar act of superiority, hence the name Project Annihilation.
This is also possibly the first server to have actual runescape product implemented into it such as , skillcape emotes and real npc actions and more real real real! This will be one of the most unique servers you will play in a lifetime. It has been in production for over 6 months and counting.[/b]
[B]:features:[/B]
[b]-It will have over 600 unique npcs all with thier unique drops.
- There will be at least 10 quests and these quests will be almost exactly like runescape, with cut-scenes and more!
- The base is so stable it will be able to hold over 2000 people on a normal dedicated server of only 4gb ram. [/b] [b] -Minigames will be awsome! The minigames will be 100% like rs or as close as possible! There will be minigames for skillers too like the trawler fishing minigame.
-Combat will very well done, it will have all working weapon specs and hit styles and more! it will have working enchanted rings, most range weapons will work, multi barrage, tele group , and lunar tele group and home teleport much much more!
-Tutorial Island Never been done before tutorial island, It will be perfect just like it was in runescape before.
-Boss monsters All boss mosters will be as good as possible, they will have the correct attack emotes, attack speeds and have very nice drops!
-Shops There will be over 100 shops to choose from, yes 100, we have made it possible!
-Adventure Every where you go you will be able to pickup stuff, like the cabbage field from rimmington and lumbridge, You will also be able to pick and spin flax just like in runescape!
-Highscores AS all of you know when there's a server there is compitition and this is the best server for it! with an xp rate of *x10* you will be able to rank your self gradually on the highscores board on our fourms.
-Skills The skill on this server will be absolutely flawless, made with precision and accuracy we will provide you with skills that look so good you will not be able to tell the difference.
-Moderation Moderators will be very friendly and will not harrass any players, moderators will be chosen by how kindly they treat and help players and also their knowledge about the server. [/b] --- Server Specs--- Base: Hyperion Revision : 459 [b] Release:[/b] When we feel that the server is ready to be released, we will inform you.
